&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>clash代理在Google Play Store下载时失败</title><link>/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Aug 2021 17:21:47 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-09-35.png" alt="Featured image of post clash代理在Google Play Store下载时失败" />&lt;p>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-14-35.png"
width="353"
height="136"
srcset="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-14-35_hu_97df052f4e172299.png 480w, /posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-14-35_hu_45cfe7916d7e2a42.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="259"
data-flex-basis="622px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>clash透明代理使用规则发现GOOGLE PLAY商店下载应用一直处于等待中，全局代理能够正常下载。在我的oneplus3t上是可以正常使用play商店的，但是在redmi k40上只能浏览，无法下载，一直处于pending状态。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-06-18.gif"
width="354"
height="356"
srcset="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-06-18_hu_4dbd1f2cdc3b6853.gif 480w, /posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-06-18_hu_9d542237083ac5a0.gif 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="99"
data-flex-basis="238px"
>
&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/play-store-failed-to-download-in-clash-proxy/2021-08-09-18-09-35.png"
